# The API reads from the ONE central env file. There is no separate api env.
#
# Compose:   it's injected automatically (see infra/.env.example + Makefile `ENV`).
# Host-run:  point at the same central file from apps/api, e.g.
#              uv run --env-file ../../.env uvicorn app.main:app --reload
#            or symlink it:   ln -s ../../.env .env
#
# Template + all variables:  ../../infra/.env.example
